data.description: This Sea Pines home did not flood during Hurricane Idalia.  Not one drop of water in the house.  The house sets a little uphill from the road, I am sure that helps.  Sea Pines has an optional HOA, no mandatory fees.  2 bedroom 2 baths with a one car garage (2 car driveway).  1,162 sq. ft. of living area.  Roof and AC are approximately 3 years old.  Water Heater is new in October 2023.  The floor plan features a nice sized living room in the front, dining and kitchen in the middle and a family room with vaulted ceilings in the rear.  The family room has sliding glass doors out to the screen enclosed and covered lanai which is good sized 11’ X 16’.  The rear yard is fenced.  Inside the home, there is laminate flooring throughout with ceramic tile in the kitchen and baths.  Great Hudson location convenient to everything!  Please take a moment and view all the professional photos and virtual tour.
